ActCorrections and Conditional Release Act
SubjectTransfer of Parole Jurisdiction Agreement with the Governments of Ontario and Quebec
PrecisOrder approving that the Minister of Public Safety and Emergency Preparedness, on behalf of her Majesty the Queen, enter into an agreement with the provinces of ONTARIO AND QUEBEC, in order to provide direction concerning the TRANSFER OF PAROLE JURISDICTION FOR OFFENDERS.
